                          <desc>
                          <locus target="#127v #128r"/> One Miracle of Michael, Tä’ammǝrä Mika’el, How God gave wealth to a certain man who had honored the feast day of Saint Michael though his farm had been destroyed by a devouring worm.
                          </desc>
                        </item>
